description: Dr. Jasmine learns more about the other members of the super-powered team she is supposed to be leading.
name: A Slight Difference Of Opionion

description: Having recieved information at the fort Altum Rhenum concerning a mission to the extreme north of the Roman Empire, Alix and Enak are excited. A mysterious expedition is prepared, led by the merchant Falcalus the tribune Carbo Tullius as they will embark upon a journey to the Baltic Sea to collect amber. But the barbarians are lurking and planning their deadly ambushes. The expedition ends in tragedy, and only our heroes and a few men come back alive.
name: Les Barbares

description: First part of the 3 Formules Du Professeur Satō storyline which was initially published periodically in Le Journal De Tintin from October 5 1971 to May 1972 before being collected as album by Le Lombard in 1977 and republished by Les Editions Blake Et Mortimer in 1990. It was the last album completed by series creator E.P. Jacobs before his death.
name: Les 3 Formules du Professeur Satō Tome 1: Mortimer à Tokyo

volume.name: Les Aventures De Blake Et Mortimer

description: Lady S., aka Shania, leads the unassuming life of an Estonian interpreter at the European Parliament in Strasbourg. Unexpected cicumstances force her to leave for Lisbon, under the CIA's orders. A major surprise awaits her there. But what she doesn't know is that when she left Strasbourg, she took a CD-Rom filled with coveted data with her, making her the target of dangerous Islamic terrorists.
name: Salade Portugaise

description: Washington DC. A top secret file from the Oval Office is found next to the lifeless body of the Russian embassy's driver. With only a few days to go till the Russian-American summit, the presence of said file in that particular place seems to indicate that a mole has infiltrated the White House. The F.B.I. doesn't need any more excuses to look into the pasts of the President's closest collaborators, including James Fitzroy, the President's secret lover, but also the adopted father of Suzan, aka Shania, aka Lady S.
name: Une Taupe à Washington
